graph TD
    subgraph "Build Process (Maven + Jib)"
        Src[Source Code] --> Maven[Maven Build]
        Maven --> Jib[Jib Plugin]
        Jib --> Image[Docker Image: classroom-crb:latest]
    end

    subgraph "Runtime (Docker Compose)"
        Compose[docker-compose.yml] --> AppService[App Service (Port 8089)]
        Compose --> DBService[MySQL Service (Port 3306)]
        AppService -- "JDBC Link" --> DBService
    end

    Image --> AppService
